#: inc/settings.php:105
msgid ""
"Your JPG/PNG images will be automatically converted to WebP. To avoid broken "
"links, please check and update any places where you've hard-coded JPG/PNG "
"URLs (e.g. image blocks, custom HTML, CSS, or shortcodes)."
